OL,3,CNo further action over military truck
OL,4,Ccrash which killed 70-year-old man
OL,6,FTwo men who were investigated after a
OL,7,Ffatal crash involving a mobility
OL,8,Fscooter and a military truck have been
OL,9,Freleased without charge.
OL,11,F70-year-old John Robert Mitchell's
OL,12,Fscooter collided with the truck near
OL,13,FColburn, close to the British Army
OL,14,Fbase at Catterick Garrison, in June
OL,15,F2025.
OL,17,FHe died while being airlifted to
OL,18,Fhospital.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
