OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1780683078
OL,3,CNo further action over military truck
OL,4,Ccrash which killed 70-year-old man
OL,6,FNorth Yorkshire Police said no further
OL,7,Faction would be taken against the two
OL,8,Fmen who were in the military truck at
OL,9,Fthe time.
OL,11,F"An extensive collision investigation
OL,12,Fhas been completed into the tragic
OL,13,Fdeath of Mr Mitchell.
OL,15,F"It concluded that no further action
OL,16,Fwill be taken against the two men who
OL,17,Fwere in the military truck. They have
OL,18,Fbeen released without charge."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
