PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1780683078
OL,3,CNo further action over military truck
OL,4,Ccrash which killed 70-year-old man
OL,6,FThe statement continue: "All parties
OL,7,Fhave been updated, and the matter has
OL,8,Fbeen passed to the Coroner."
OL,10,FMr Mitchell was described by his
OL,11,Ffamily as a "much loved husband,
OL,12,Fbrother, uncle and godfather" who
OL,13,Fwould be "sadly missed".
